		{"id":"ff74b2c91e13743a","type":"text","text":" [Table 3](https://iopscience.iop.org/0004-637X/907/2/67/suppdata/apjabca9at3_ascii.txt?doi=10.3847/1538-4357/abca9a) HAWC Power-law Fits and Significances for the Revised Sample of 136 AGNs from the 3FHL Catalog\n\n3FHL Source\tCounterpart\tClass\tRedshift\tTS\t$\\pm \\sqrt{\\mathrm{TS}}$\tK +or- DeltaK\tK_2sigma\t\n(1)\t(2)\t(3)\t(4)\t(5)\t(6)\t(7)\t(8)\t\nJ0007.9+4711\tRX J0007.9+4711\tbll\t0.2800\t-4.49\t-2.12\t-31.9 +or- 15.1\t9.16\t\nJ0013.8-1855\tRBS 0030\tbll\t0.0949\t-0.10\t-0.32\t-2.20 +or- 6.81\t11.5\t\nJ0018.6+2946\tRBS 0042\tbll\t0.1000\t+0.01\t+0.11\t+0.10 +or- 0.93\t1.97\t\nJ0037.8+1239\tNVSS J003750+123818\tbll\t0.0890\t+0.47\t+0.69\t+0.52 +or- 0.76\t2.03\t\nJ0047.9+3947\tB3 0045+395\tbll\t0.2520\t-0.18\t-0.42\t-2.68 +or- 6.38\t10.3\t\nJ0056.3-0936\tTXS 0053-098\tbll\t0.1031\t-0.21\t-0.46\t-1.33 +or- 2.88\t4.53\t\nJ0059.3-0152\t1RXS J005916.3-015030\tbll\t0.1440\t+0.95\t+0.98\t+2.61 +or- 2.67\t7.93\t\nJ0112.1+2245\tS2 0109+22\tBLL\t0.2650\t+0.33\t+0.57\t+1.99 +or- 3.47\t8.88\t\nJ0123.0+3422\t1ES 0120+340\tbll\t0.2720\t+6.53\t+2.56\t+13.1 +or- 5.13\t23.4\t\nJ0131.1+5546\tTXS 0128+554\tbcu\t0.0365\t-0.85\t-0.92\t-1.61 +or- 1.75\t2.10\t\nJ0152.6+0147\tPMN J0152+0146\tbll\t0.0800\t-0.89\t-0.94\t-0.89 +or- 0.94\t1.10\t\nJ0159.5+1047\tRX J0159.5+1047\tbll\t0.1950\t+1.09\t+1.04\t+2.52 +or- 2.41\t7.31\t\nJ0211.2+1051\tMG1 J021114+1051\tBLL\t0.2000\t-0.58\t-0.76\t-1.92 +or- 2.51\t3.26\t\nJ0214.5+5145\tTXS 0210+515\tbll\t0.0490\t+2.63\t+1.62\t+2.43 +or- 1.51\t5.43\t\nJ0216.4+2315\tRBS 0298\tbll\t0.2880\t-0.08\t-0.29\t-1.14 +or- 3.97\t6.74\t\nJ0217.1+0836\tZS 0214+083\tbll\t0.0850\t+4.58\t+2.14\t+1.70 +or- 0.80\t3.31\t\nJ0219.1-1723\t1RXS J021905.8-172503\tbll\t0.1287\t+0.01\t+0.10\t+1.0 +or- 9.9\t20.9\t\nJ0232.8+2017\t1ES 0229+200\tbll\t0.1400\t-0.28\t-0.53\t-0.70 +or- 1.32\t1.98\t\nJ0242.7-0002\tNGC 1068\tsbg\t0.0038\t+1.45\t+1.21\t+0.24 +or- 0.20\t0.65","x":-217,"y":-2407,"width":756,"height":341},
		{"id":"1f71f5295f654324","type":"text","text":"[data.hawc-observatory.org/datasets/3hwc-survey/3HWC_combined.yml](https://data.hawc-observatory.org/datasets/3hwc-survey/3HWC_combined.yml)\n3HWC Catalog. This file includes all information provided in tables 1-3 of the accompanying paper.  \nAngles are in degrees.\nFluxes are reported at 7 TeV and are in TeV-1 cm-2 s-1.\n\n2HWC: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, 2HWC J0534+220]\n    - [dist, 0.0]\n    - [RA, 83.6279]\n    - [Dec, 22.0243]\n  ATNF_PSR: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, B0531+21]\n    - [dist, 0.01100680102937859]\n    - [RA, 83.63322]\n    - [Dec, 22.01446]\n    - [Age, 1260.0]\n    - [Edot, 4.5e+38]\n    - [Distance, 2.0]\n  Dec: 22.0243\n  FGL: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, 4FGL J0534.5+2201i]\n    - [tevcat, 'Crab            ']\n    - [dist, 0.0063927658471547]\n    - [RA, 83.63300323486328]\n    - [Dec, 22.020000457763672]\n    - [class, 'PWN  ']\n  FHL: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, '3FHL J0534.5+2201 ']\n    - [tevcat, 'Crab Nebula     ']\n    - [dist, 0.008203749981499165]\n    - [RA, 83.63483428955078]\n    - [Dec, 22.019203186035156]\n    - [class, 'PWN    ']\n  RA: 83.6279\n  SNRCat: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, G184.6-05.8]\n    - [dist, 0.007723125777331253]\n    - [RA, 83.62916666666665]\n    - [Dec, 22.016666666666666]\n    - [Type, filled-centre]\n  TS: 35736.499681\n  b: -5.78316902993781\n  flux measurements:\n  - {flux: 2.34204e-13, flux systematic down: -3.402997237965378e-14, flux systematic up: 5.524898950351944e-14,\n    flux uncertainty down: -1.40228e-15, flux uncertainty up: 1.40459e-15, index: -2.57949,\n    index systematic down: -0.018368070121817157, index systematic up: 0.06690214196869962,\n    index uncertainty down: -0.00465478, index uncertainty up: 0.00465904, tested radius: 0.0}\n  l: 184.54655248643084\n  name: 3HWC J0534+220\n  position uncertainty: 0.05725810686362343\n  search radius: 0.0\n  tevcat: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, Crab Pulsar]\n    - [dist, 0.01084755009295374]\n    - [RA, 83.63291666666666]\n    - [Dec, 22.0145]\n    - [class, PSR]\n- ATNF_PSR: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, B0540+23]\n    - [dist, 0.8395606332786264]\n    - [RA, 85.79025]\n    - [Dec, 23.48472]\n    - [Age, 253000.0]\n    - [Edot, 4.1e+34]\n    - [Distance, 1.56]\n  Dec: 22.8719\n  FGL: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, '4FGL J0544.4+2238 ']\n    - [tevcat, '                ']\n    - [dist, 0.8997839552173199]\n    - [RA, 86.10929870605469]\n    - [Dec, 22.641799926757812]\n    - [class, '     ']\n  RA: 85.166\n  TS: 28.83797401\n  b: -4.128534019025944\n  flux measurements:\n  - {flux: 4.7558e-15, flux systematic down: -8.119131807650368e-16, flux systematic up: 1.1274867328709466e-15,\n    flux uncertainty down: -7.59367e-16, flux uncertainty up: 7.22962e-16, index: -2.8396,\n    index systematic down: -0.033824130439672674, index systematic up: 0.14373974711262028,\n    index uncertainty down: -0.142449, index uncertainty up: 0.1431, tested radius: 0.0}\n  l: 184.58335953841944\n  name: 3HWC J0540+228\n  position uncertainty: 0.1117493194053931\n  search radius: 0.0\n  tevcat: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, HAWC J0543+233]\n    - [dist, 0.7730979360817953]\n    - [RA, 85.78]\n    - [Dec, 23.4]\n    - [class, TeV Halo]\n- ATNF_PSR: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, B0540+23]\n    - [dist, 0.36981342122033334]\n    - [RA, 85.79025]\n    - [Dec, 23.48472]\n    - [Age, 253000.0]\n    - [Edot, 4.1e+34]\n    - [Distance, 1.56]\n  Dec: 23.115\n  FGL: !!python/object/apply:collections.OrderedDict\n  - - [assoc, '4FGL J0544.4+2238 ']\n    - [tevcat, '                ']\n    - [dist, 0.5615117259718984]\n    - [RA, 86.10929870605469]\n    - [Dec, 22.64179992